hopobject.body: There's a three month trial period valentus uk launch His voice seemed to crack as he explained how he had let his teammates and coaches down in the heartbreaking 27-21 loss to the Bears. There were no tears, but the six straight losses and 15 interceptions to open the season have clearly gotten to him. He seems to go out of his way not to let anybody see how the game affects him emotionally, but his failures this season have become a huge burden to carry around and he was hiding his feelings no more.
